<!-- My services section -->
<section class="my-services section" id="services">
    <div class="section__content">
        <h2 class="section__title-light section__title--services fade-in">What I do</h2>
        <div class="services fade-in">
            <div class="service">
                <h3>AI-Powered Web Applications</h3>
                <p>Designing and delivering AI-driven applications where large language models are integrated as structured system
                    components, not simple API add-ons. I build Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) pipelines, semantic search layers,
                    and agent-based workflows using Python and modern full-stack technologies. My focus is on deterministic
                    orchestration, cost control, and production-grade reliability within scalable architectures.</p>

            </div>
            <!-- /service -->
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Full-Stack Web Development</h3>
                <p>Architecting and implementing scalable full-stack systems using Next.js, React, Node.js, and modern database
                    infrastructures. I work across the entire application lifecycle, from API design and authentication flows to cloud
                    deployment and performance optimization, applying clean architecture principles and strong typing to ensure
                    maintainability and long-term scalability.</p>

            </div>
            <!-- /service -->
            <div class="service">
                <h3>API Design & Database Architecture</h3>
                <p>Designing robust APIs and data architectures for both traditional and AI-enhanced systems. Experienced in PostgreSQL
                    (including pgvector for AI workloads), MongoDB, and multi-tenant architectures with Row-Level Security. I emphasize
                    data integrity, performance tuning, security enforcement, and structured validation to support enterprise-ready
                    applications.</p>

            </div>
            <!-- /service -->
        </div>
        <!-- /services -->
        <a href="#work" class="btn">My Work</a>
    </div>
